data.description: IMPROVED PRICE! Large 4 bedroom, 2 full bath home located in the Twin Oaks neighborhood. You will enjoy the spacious rooms, hardwood floors and double-sided fire place in the living room and family room. Large kitchen with adjoining dining room. Main level laundry off kitchen. Primary bedroom features En Suite bathroom. The inviting backyard is perfect for enjoying summer evenings with patio, mature trees and playset. Conveniently located to Routes 30 and 15 and close to parks and playgrounds. Large basement ready for your finishing touches. ATTENTION VETERANS - this home has a VA Assumable Mortgage! A one-year American Home Shield Warranty is included. Come See!
